 check network public-network with interface eth0
   group system
   if failed  link then alert
   if changed link then alert
   if saturation     > 50%    for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if download       > 5 MB/s for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if upload         > 5 MB/s for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if total download > 20 GB   in last hour then alert
   if total upload   > 20 GB   in last hour then alert
   if total download > 50 GB  in last day then alert
   if total upload   > 50 GB  in last day then alert

 check network private-network with interface eth1
   group system
   if failed  link then alert
   if changed link then alert
   if saturation     > 50%    for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if download       > 5 MB/s for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if upload         > 5 MB/s for 5 times within 15 cycles then alert
   if total download > 20 GB   in last hour then alert
   if total upload   > 20 GB   in last hour then alert
   if total download > 50 GB  in last day then alert
   if total upload   > 50 GB  in last day then alert
